These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, water
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, salsa
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking water is between the fan of salsa and the person drinking 7up##2
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | 7up | water | fanta |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | dubstep    | salsa   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, reading, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, accountant, freelancer
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the freelancer is between the photographer and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | chess    | writing        | reading |
| Job     | accountant | freelancer | photographer         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, coffee
3 different pets are kept: cat, snake, goat
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the owner of the snake and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice     | coffee |
| Pet        | snake  | goat | cat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, disco
3 different pets are kept: goat, horse, mouse
1. the fan of ambient is the owner of the goat##1
2. the fan of disco is between the owner of the horse and the owner of the goat##2
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | disco     | ambient |
| Pet           | horse | mouse | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, card-games, video-games
3 different pets are kept: turtle, cat, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | card-games | video-games     | gardening |
| Pet     | guinea-pig    | turtle | cat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, german
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, lacrosse, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the german and the american##2
2. the american is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the indonesian is on the right of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | american  | indonesian   | german        |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pear, pomegranate
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, italian, russian
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the indian is between the person eating pomegranate and the italian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | pear  | eggplant  | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | italian | indian | russian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, sports, thriller
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, russian, indonesian
1. the person watching sports movies is the indonesian##1
2. the russian is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller   | adventure  | sports  |
| Nationality   | indian | russian | indonesian |

