.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, handball, soccer
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, van, train
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | soccer | tennis | handball  |
| Transport   | train    | scooter        | van |

