.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, coffee
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, pineapple, cauliflower
1. the person eating cauliflower is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating pumpkin##2
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda      | coffee      |
| Food       | pineapple  | cauliflower | pumpkin |

