2. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | hip-hop   | punk   |
| Sport         | water-polo | cycling | ice-hockey |

